      &MT
        REL_CUTOFF 1.5
      &END MT
      POISSON_SOLVER MT
      PERIODIC NONE
    &END POISSON
  &END DFT
  &SUBSYS
    &CELL
      ABC 6.0 6.0 6.0
      PERIODIC NONE
    &END CELL
    &COORD
