 H        -0.4939080000        -1.7112430000        -0.7610180000
 H        -0.4939080000        -1.7112430000         0.7612180000
    &END COORD
    &KIND H
      BASIS_SET aug-QZV3P-GTH
      POTENTIAL GTH-HCTH120-q1
      AUX_BASIS_SET aux-scp
      ALPHA_SCP 1.0
      I_SCP .5
    &END KIND
